<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV67">
<l>kāviyu nīlamum vēluṅ kayalum palapalaveṉ</l>
<l>ṟāviyiṉ taṉmai yaḷavalla pārip pacurarceṟṟa</l>
<l>māviyam puḷvalla mātavaṉ kōvintaṉ vēṅkaṭañcēr</l>
<l>tūviyam pēṭaiyaṉ ṉāḷkaṇka ḷāya tuṇaimalarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“They are many things: lotuses, blue water-lilies, spears and carps”,</l>
<l>they are not in the measure of [my] soul’s power – the paired blossoms</l>
<l>that are the eyes of her like a feathery she-bird joining the Vēṅkaṭam of Kōvintaṉ,</l>
<l>Mātavaṉ, strong with the big obedient bird who resisted the weighty Asuras.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
